# Vox Terminal — Project Conventions

## Stack
- Python 3.10+, hatchling build, `pip install -e ".[dev,vad]"`
- CLI: typer + rich, entry point `vox_terminal.cli:app_main`
- Config: pydantic-settings (env `VOX_TERMINAL_*` + `vox-terminal.toml`)
- LLM: Anthropic Claude, STT: faster-whisper/OpenAI, TTS: macOS say/ElevenLabs/OpenAI
- Testing: pytest + pytest-asyncio, `asyncio_mode = "auto"`
- Linting: ruff (line-length 100), mypy (strict), pre-commit

## Key Paths
- Source: `src/vox_terminal/`
- Tests: `tests/` (unit/, integration/, contracts/)
- Config: `pyproject.toml`

## Commits
Use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/):
- `feat(tts): add ElevenLabs streaming`
- `fix(audio): handle PortAudio errors`
- `test(llm): add timeout contract`
- `docs: update configuration table`
